data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! MOTIVATED SELLERS. Welcome Home! This home is located in West Edmond within minutes of the schools. This quiet neighborhood is tucked back off the main street. As you step inside to be welcomed by a spacious living room for entertaining. A dedicated study is to that features a built-in book cases and a private gaming nook with a built-in desk. Large kitchen is open to the family dining and a separate living space that has ample counter space, abundant cabinet storage, oversized pantry. The Master bedroom is very spacious with a two walk-in closets. The Master bathroom has been completely upgraded with a stand alone tub and walk in shower. The backyard is perfect for entertaining offering a covered patio that faces the beautiful back yard w/ spectacular 2-tiered deck with seasonal views of neighborhood pond. Upstairs includes three rooms plus the bonus room and a full bath. Neighborhood common area has a stocked pond, walking trail, picnic areas and a basketball court  Buyer to verify lot size, square footage and schools. Home also includes new HVAC and water filtration system.
